11
00:00:15,871 --> 00:00:17,851
這幅拉斐爾我可沒忘
And I haven't forgotten about the Raphael.

12
00:00:18,511 --> 00:00:19,811
尼爾的信件裡有密碼
Neal coded his letters.

13
00:00:19,841 --> 00:00:20,941
我們破譯了
And we cracked it.

14
00:00:21,551 --> 00:00:23,741
還不知道是什麼意思  不過會查到的
Don't know what they mean yet, but we will.

15
00:00:24,251 --> 00:00:25,411
-我是...  -克雷默探員
- I'm --  - Agent Kramer.

16
00:00:25,411 --> 00:00:27,101
華盛頓藝品犯罪科主管
Head of the bureau's D.C. Art Crimes Unit.

17
00:00:27,101 --> 00:00:29,371
這麼說彼得的能耐都是跟您學的
So you're the one who taught Peter everything he knows.

18
00:00:29,371 --> 00:00:32,161
你我相見是早晚的事  卡夫瑞先生
I'd say this moment was inevitable, Mr. Caffrey.

19
00:00:32,161 --> 00:00:34,351
-尼爾是我的線人  -也是你的朋友
- Neal's my C.I.  - He's also a friend.

20
00:00:34,471 --> 00:00:36,501
你覺得騙子永遠不會悔改
You think once a con, always a con?

21
00:00:36,501 --> 00:00:39,261
我認為他們遭殃時你得保護自己
I think you have to protect yourself when they fall.

22
00:00:39,971 --> 00:00:40,981
寶藏在你手裡
You have the treasure.

23
00:00:40,981 --> 00:00:42,621
-我沒偷  -你個混蛋
- I didn't steal it.  - You son of a bitch!

24
00:00:42,631 --> 00:00:44,381
我不管  反正在你手裡
I don't care. You have it.

25
00:00:44,721 --> 00:00:45,461
東西在哪
Where is it?

26
00:00:45,671 --> 00:00:46,751
本來就在這裡
It was here.

27
00:00:46,991 --> 00:00:47,841
他把東西轉移了
He already moved it.

28
00:00:47,841 --> 00:00:49,521
蚊子  當然是他
Mozzie? Of course it was Mozzie.

29
00:00:49,521 --> 00:00:51,291
我沒想到他動作這麼快
I didn't think he'd move it this fast.

30
00:00:51,291 --> 00:00:52,071
這是什麼
What is it?

31
00:00:52,081 --> 00:00:54,671
這是封來自美國緩刑局的信
This is a letter from the U.S. Probation Office.

32
00:00:54,841 --> 00:00:57,131
因為你的傑出貢獻
"Because of your outstanding service,

33
00:00:57,131 --> 00:00:58,861
包括奪回寶藏
"Including recovering the treasure

34
00:00:58,861 --> 00:01:00,051
抓捕凱勒歸案
"and catching Keller,

35
00:01:00,471 --> 00:01:03,221
