"The U.S. Probation office is convening a hearing

36
00:01:03,221 --> 00:01:06,271
討論對於你的減刑事宜
to discuss the commutation of your sentence."

37
00:01:06,271 --> 00:01:07,151
這是什麼意思
What's that mean?

38
00:01:07,381 --> 00:01:09,091
說明你不用戴腳環了
It means no anklet.

39
00:01:09,801 --> 00:01:10,711
不再受監控
No nothing.

40
00:01:10,711 --> 00:01:12,081
你就要自由了
You could be a free man.

41
00:01:17,321 --> 00:01:19,091
請正式陳述你的姓名
State your name for the record, please.

42
00:01:19,671 --> 00:01:21,351
