Neal George Caffrey.

43
00:01:21,391 --> 00:01:23,931
卡夫瑞先生  你清楚今天為什麼請你來嗎
Mr. Caffrey, do you understand why you're sitting here today?

44
00:01:24,221 --> 00:01:25,161
清楚
I do.

45
00:01:25,761 --> 00:01:28,331
聯邦檢察署為我申請了第35條
The U.S. Attorney has petitioned a rule 35 motion

46
00:01:28,331 --> 00:01:30,491
假釋動議  如果獲得批准
on my behalf, which, if granted,

47
00:01:30,581 --> 00:01:33,281
將減免我的刑期  並具結釋放
would commute my sentence and set about my own recognizance.

48
00:01:33,311 --> 00:01:36,131
簡言之  你們想知道我是否有資格獲得自由
In essence, you want to know if I've earned my freedom.

49
00:01:36,901 --> 00:01:38,161
看來你已經研究過了
You've done your homework.

50
00:01:38,581 --> 00:01:39,591
是的  長官
Yes, ma'am.

51
00:01:40,171 --> 00:01:42,931
在四年刑期中你已經服刑兩年
You've already served two years of a four-year sentence

52
00:01:42,991 --> 00:01:45,411
