103
00:03:45,321 --> 00:03:47,491
我是罪犯  不過是非著名
I am a felon, but I'm not known --

104
00:03:47,491 --> 00:03:49,251
至少在司法圈非著名
at least in bureaucratic circles.

105
00:03:49,251 --> 00:03:50,331
我承認
I stand corrected.

106
00:03:50,771 --> 00:03:52,551
而且已經有很多人來支持我了
But I've already got plenty of people on my side.

107
00:03:52,551 --> 00:03:55,471
伊利莎白  瓊  還有莎拉
Elizabeth, June...Sara.

108
00:03:55,541 --> 00:03:56,601
-真的  -對
- Really?  - Yeah.

109
00:03:56,801 --> 00:03:59,531
很好  那兩個小探員呢
Good. What about the demi-suits?

110
00:03:59,681 --> 00:04:02,151
瓊斯和戴安  萬能牌
Mm. Jones and Diana? Wild cards.

111
00:04:03,161 --> 00:04:04,681
那探員叔本人呢
And the suit himself?

112
00:04:05,211 --> 00:04:06,791
考慮到之前發生事情
Well, considering everything that's happened --

113
00:04:06,791 --> 00:04:08,771
關於寶藏  關於凱勒
with the treasure, with Keller --

114
00:04:09,371 --> 00:04:10,701
彼得怎麼選擇都有可能
Peter could go either way.

115
00:04:10,911 --> 00:04:12,171
你認為他決定了嗎
Think he's decided?

116
00:04:13,051 --> 00:04:14,201
我不知道
I don't know.

117
00:04:14,691 --> 00:04:15,661
等等
Hold on.

118
00:04:16,861 --> 00:04:20,401
克雷默探員  華盛頓藝品犯罪科的老爺爺
Agent Kramer, the D.C. Art Crimes grand-pere  --

119
00:04:20,401 --> 00:04:21,141
