He's speaking?

120
00:04:21,141 --> 00:04:22,981
克雷默應該只代表局裡
Kramer was supposed to submit a written report

121
00:04:22,981 --> 00:04:24,321
提交文本材料
on behalf of the bureau.

122
00:04:25,201 --> 00:04:27,471
如果他親自作證  那絕不是只走程序
If he's speaking in person, that's more than a formality.

123
00:04:27,471 --> 00:04:29,001
那對你會有什麼影響
Well, what does that do to your chances?

124
00:04:29,001 --> 00:04:31,121
我覺得不會有正面作用
Well, I can't imagine it improves them.

125
00:04:32,631 --> 00:04:34,981
反正最壞的情況是他不同意
You know what? Worst-case scenario, he says no,

126
00:04:34,981 --> 00:04:36,711
我繼續戴著腳環  跟著彼得
and I stay on the anklet with Peter.

127
00:04:37,221 --> 00:04:40,181
在每個最壞的情況之後
Well, behind every worst-case scenario,

128
00:04:40,181 --> 00:04:43,001
通常都有更壞的情況
there's a worse worst-case scenario.

129
00:04:43,051 --> 00:04:43,901
你是不是就非得
Isn't there a child

130
00:04:43,901 --> 00:04:45,451
怎麼敗興怎麼說啊
whose balloon you need to pop somewhere?

131
00:04:45,451 --> 00:04:47,811
沒錯  消極是我的習慣
Yeah. Negativity -- force of habit.

132
00:04:47,811 --> 00:04:49,701
我想  肯定沒什麼問題
I'm...sure it doesn't mean anything.

133
00:04:50,701 --> 00:04:52,491
對  沒事
Yeah. Nothing.

134
00:04:56,941 --> 00:04:58,091
進來
Come on in.

135
00:04:58,501 --> 00:04:59,541
屋裡真香
Smells good in here.

136
00:04:59,961 --> 00:05:01,431
小伊在烘焙
Yeah. El's been baking.

137
00:05:05,581 --> 00:05:08,101
恭喜減刑

138
00:05:08,101 --> 00:05:09,521
減刑慶祝蛋糕
A commutation cake.

139
00:05:09,931 --> 00:05:12,541
我告訴過她為時尚早
Yeah, I told her it was a little premature.

140
00:05:12,951 --> 00:05:14,741
親愛的  我另一個蛋糕也好了
Hey, honey. I got that other cake.

141
00:05:15,251 --> 00:05:16,451
給你看看
Wait till you see it.

142
00:05:16,921 --> 00:05:20,531
別氣餒
"Hang in there."

143
00:05:19,661 --> 00:05:21,731
別氣餒

