147
00:05:26,041 --> 00:05:27,581
-那最好  -對
- That'll be good.  - Yes.

148
00:05:27,581 --> 00:05:28,801
不管怎樣
Well, for what it's worth,

149
00:05:28,801 --> 00:05:30,351
我會選擇一號蛋糕
I'm actually voting for cake number one.

150
00:05:30,361 --> 00:05:31,391
謝謝
I appreciate that.

151
00:05:31,391 --> 00:05:32,381
你們聊
You guys talk.

152
