你決定了嗎
So, have you decided?

153
00:05:38,441 --> 00:05:40,501
我打算怎麼說嗎  說真的
What I'm gonna say? Honestly...

154
00:05:41,401 --> 00:05:42,731
沒有  還沒決定
No. I haven't.

155
00:05:43,731 --> 00:05:46,041
什麼事重要到不能打電話
So, what's so important you couldn't call?

156
00:05:47,251 --> 00:05:49,171
為什麼克雷默會參加聽證會
Why is Kramer speaking at my hearing?

157
00:05:49,631 --> 00:05:51,261
別為這個緊張
Don't let that put you on edge.

158
00:05:52,831 --> 00:05:54,641
