I'll be fine. Go.

722
00:34:21,883 --> 00:34:23,093
你背著我搞鬼
You went behind my back,

723
00:34:24,023 --> 00:34:25,963
密謀妨礙司法公正
conspired to obstruct justice.

724
00:34:26,003 --> 00:34:27,413
