I could say you did the same.

725
00:34:27,413 --> 00:34:28,903
醒醒吧  彼得  睜開眼看看吧
Wake up, Petey! Open your eyes!

726
00:34:28,963 --> 00:34:30,693
你不是他的拍檔  你是他的目標
You're not his partner. You're his mark!

727
00:34:31,123 --> 00:34:33,033
他最擅長騙取別人的信任
This boy's run such a good confidence game,

728
00:34:33,043 --> 00:34:33,893
