He's got you thinking

729
00:34:33,893 --> 00:34:35,603
這些是你想要的
that you've come out ahead in all this.

730
00:34:35,923 --> 00:34:37,993
你從什麼時候開始喪失對人性的信心了
When did you stop putting faith in people?

731
00:34:38,573 --> 00:34:39,813
從他們不配讓我相信時開始
When they stopped deserving it.

732
00:34:43,853 --> 00:34:45,083
這事兒沒完  彼得
This isn't over yet, Pete.

733
00:34:46,363 --> 00:34:47,153
