Not by a long shot.

734
00:34:57,103 --> 00:35:00,913
卡夫瑞先生  你應該獲得自由嗎
Mr. Caffrey, do you deserve to be free?

735
00:35:02,713 --> 00:35:03,703
這不是由我來決定的
That's not for me to decide.

736
00:35:05,893 --> 00:35:08,323
我不會坐在這裡給你演一出我已是
I won't sit here and give you some monologue

737
00:35:08,323 --> 00:35:09,693
如何改過自新的獨角戲
about how reformed I am.

738
00:35:10,833 --> 00:35:12,583
事實勝於雄辯
Actions speak louder than words,

739
00:35:12,963 --> 00:35:15,613
希望我在聯調局服務期間的事實
And, hopefully, my actions while in service to the FBI

740
00:35:15,623 --> 00:35:16,783
能勝於我的雄辯
say more than I can.

741
00:35:18,083 --> 00:35:20,233
那你會如何利用你的自由呢
And what would you do with your freedom?

742
00:35:21,573 --> 00:35:22,493
有一件事我可以確定
I can tell you one thing.

743
00:35:22,493 --> 00:35:25,803
短時間內我哪裡都不會去
I won't be going anywhere anytime soon.

744
00:35:26,033 --> 00:35:27,233
-哪兒都不去  -沒錯
-You won't? -No.

745
00:35:27,933 --> 00:35:28,773
我在這裡很開心
I'm happy here.

746
00:35:30,443 --> 00:35:31,783
有人曾對我說過
You know, someone once told me

747
00:35:32,723 --> 00:35:35,593
我就像生活在美夢中  只是帶了腳環
my life is a dream with an anklet attached.

748
00:35:37,483 --> 00:35:39,823
如果我明天一覺醒來而腳環還在
If I wake up tomorrow and that anklet is still on --

749
00:35:40,853 --> 00:35:43,563
我有一份好工作  一間好住宅
I have a good job, a wonderful home...

750
00:35:45,213 --> 00:35:47,343
一名拍檔  一名知己
a partner and a best friend.

751
00:35:50,093 --> 00:35:50,813
一個家
A family.

752
00:35:54,783 --> 00:35:57,803
但是醒來後  給自己的答案
But to wake up and answer only to myself...

753
00:36:02,703 --> 00:36:03,823
對我來說意味著一切
That would mean everything.

754
00:36:06,233 --> 00:36:08,243
我們要與另一位面談一下
We have one more interview to conduct

755
00:36:08,303 --> 00:36:09,533
然後再做出決定
before we make our decision.

756
00:36:09,643 --> 00:36:12,023
今天下午五點前通知你答案
You'll have an answer here today by 5:00 p.m.

757
00:36:12,453 --> 00:36:13,093
謝謝
Thank you.

758
00:36:17,793 --> 00:36:18,553
情況怎麼樣
How'd it go?

759
00:36:19,753 --> 00:36:21,273
我感覺就那樣吧
As well as it could go, I think.

760
00:36:23,013 --> 00:36:24,253
你知道最棒的是什麼嗎
You know what the nice thing is?

761
00:36:26,233 --> 00:36:26,983
已經不重要了
It doesn't matter.

762
00:36:27,723 --> 00:36:28,393
什麼意思
What do you mean?

763
00:36:28,873 --> 00:36:30,633
你會走進去作證
You're gonna go in there and say your piece,

764
00:36:30,633 --> 00:36:32,063
委員會會作出決定
and the board's gonna make their decision.

765
00:36:33,283 --> 00:36:34,723
但不管有沒有腳環
But with or without my anklet,

766
00:36:35,173 --> 00:36:37,263
到了週一早上  我會走出電梯
come Monday morning, I'm gonna step off that elevator

767
00:36:37,263 --> 00:36:38,763
踏入21層的辦公室  開始工作
on the 21st floor and go to work.

768
00:36:42,343 --> 00:36:44,333
你曾對說我  你從未騙過我
You once told me you never lied to me

769
00:36:44,333 --> 00:36:45,183
也永遠不會騙我
and you never will.

770
00:36:45,653 --> 00:36:46,873
現在我想知道一件事
So I need to know something.

771
00:36:49,173 --> 00:36:52,023
克雷默和我第一次為德加畫作查你的時候
The first time Kramer and I went after you for the Degas,

772
00:36:53,223 --> 00:36:54,243
你是怎麼換掉畫作的
How'd you switch the paintings?

773
00:36:58,603 --> 00:37:00,993
我偷溜進頂層  偷梁換柱
I snuck up to the penthouse, pulled the swap,

774
00:37:00,993 --> 00:37:03,353
從樓頂跳傘  在華爾街著陸
then base-jumped off the building and landed on Wall Street.

775
00:37:05,883 --> 00:37:07,123
好吧  你沒說過
Fine. Don't tell me.

776
00:37:11,183 --> 00:37:11,953
我得走了
I got to go in.

777
00:37:15,074 --> 00:37:16,804
你在羅斯福島見的那個人
That person you saw on Roosevelt Island --

778
00:37:17,534 --> 00:37:18,104
是誰
Who was it?

779
00:37:21,924 --> 00:37:22,664
這事結束後
When this is over...

780
00:37:24,254 --> 00:37:25,234
我會全告訴我
I'll tell you everything.

781
00:37:28,604 --> 00:37:29,324
回見
See you soon.

782
00:37:57,094 --> 00:37:58,564
他們已經在等你了  博爾克探員
They're ready for you now, Agent Burke.

783
00:37:59,264 --> 00:38:00,044
謝了  亨利
Thanks, henry.

784
00:38:02,024 --> 00:38:02,804
這是幹什麼
What is this?

785
00:38:03,684 --> 00:38:05,584
這幾位執法官在等著尼爾·卡夫瑞一回來
These marshals are here to take Neal Caffrey

786
00:38:05,594 --> 00:38:06,944
就把他送進監獄
into custody when he returns.

787
00:38:07,764 --> 00:38:08,514
為了什麼
For what?

788
00:38:08,664 --> 00:38:10,134
你要是聽進去我的話就知道了
If you had only listened to me.

789
00:38:10,284 --> 00:38:12,424
-為了什麼  -危害公眾利益
- For what? - Public endangerment.

790
00:38:13,054 --> 00:38:14,814
我們有一堆證人能證明
I've got a dozen eyewitnesses

791
00:38:14,924 --> 00:38:16,624
他從纜車上跳了下來
who saw Caffrey hop that tram.

792
00:38:17,114 --> 00:38:21,144
再加上躲避逮捕  妨礙司法公正
Combine that with evading arrest, obstruction of justice.

793
00:38:21,144 --> 00:38:23,924
管他呢  也許再加條"亂穿馬路罪"來湊數
Hell, I may even throw in a jaywalking charge for good measure

794
00:38:24,314 --> 00:38:25,954
我們的工作可不是復仇
We're not in the revenge business.

795
00:38:26,424 --> 00:38:28,774
尼爾惹到你了  你就想傷害他
Neal pissed you off, and now you want to hurt him.

796
00:38:28,914 --> 00:38:29,764
只是要控制他
Just control him.

797
00:38:30,444 --> 00:38:31,944
尼爾有一堆的把柄
Neal's got a lot of skeletons.

798
00:38:32,244 --> 00:38:34,484
我抓住一塊  讓他套上腳環
I'll pick one, slap that anklet on him,

799
00:38:34,564 --> 00:38:36,974
就能讓他永遠留在華盛頓為我工作了
And he'll work for me in D.C. permanently.

800
00:38:39,554 --> 00:38:42,504
你明白這其實對大家都好  明白嗎
You understand this is best for everyone, don't you?

801
00:38:58,064 --> 00:38:58,704
明白嗎
Don't you?

802
00:39:02,424 --> 00:39:03,724
我要去作陳述了
I have a statement to make.

803
00:39:07,454 --> 00:39:09,414
請正式陳述你的姓名和
State your name and relationship to Neal Caffrey

804
00:39:09,414 --> 00:39:10,524
與尼爾·卡夫瑞的關係
for the record, please.

805
00:39:11,044 --> 00:39:12,484
特別探員彼得·博爾克
Special Agent Peter Burke.

806
00:39:12,704 --> 00:39:15,274
自從尼爾·卡夫瑞的監管權轉移過來後
I've been Neal Caffrey's handler at the Federal

807
00:39:15,294 --> 00:39:18,324
我一直是他在聯邦調查局的管理人
Bureau of Investigation since his release into our custody

808
00:39:18,904 --> 00:39:19,784
你抓到的他嗎
You caught him?

809
00:39:20,244 --> 00:39:21,054
抓了兩次
Twice.

810
00:39:21,914 --> 00:39:24,294
你們應該瞭解  上次我抓到他時
And you should know, the last time I caught him,

811
00:39:24,834 --> 00:39:26,914
他孤零零地坐在空蕩蕩的公寓裡
he was sitting alone in an empty apartment.

812
00:39:27,114 --> 00:39:28,584
一無所有  無親無故
He had nothing. No one.

813
00:39:29,134 --> 00:39:29,874
現在呢
And now?

814
00:39:30,214 --> 00:39:32,514
他擁有了人生  在這裡有了真正的生活
He has a life. A real life here.

815
00:39:33,304 --> 00:39:36,014
可以讓他腳踏實地  過體面的生活
One that keeps him grounded and decent.

816
00:39:36,644 --> 00:39:37,314
正如你們所聽到的
As you've heard,

817
00:39:37,314 --> 00:39:39,254
有很多人關心尼爾
there are many people who care about Neal,

818
00:39:39,334 --> 00:39:41,914
而不只是把他視為一名罪犯
people who see him as more than just a criminal.

819
00:39:42,964 --> 00:39:44,464
我承認他會令我沮喪
He's frustrating, I'll admit.

820
00:39:44,464 --> 00:39:46,274
有時候會氣得我發瘋
He drives me crazy on his best days.

821
00:39:46,824 --> 00:39:48,534
我並不能永遠知道尼爾在哪裡
I don't always have to know where Neal is

822
00:39:48,534 --> 00:39:49,424
他想做什麼
or what he's up to.

823
00:39:49,514 --> 00:39:52,814
但我知道  他有一顆善良的心
But I do know that he has a good heart

824
00:39:54,394 --> 00:39:55,774
有原則
and a set of principles...

825
00:39:55,884 --> 00:39:57,774
而六年前  當他只是扔到我桌子上
That weren't there six years ago when

826
00:39:57,784 --> 00:40:00,384
某案卷的嫌犯時  他並沒有這個
he was just another case file that got dropped on my desk.

827
00:40:01,734 --> 00:40:03,874
你以為卡夫瑞先生已經改過自新了嗎
Do you think Mr. Caffrey is reformed?

828
00:40:05,514 --> 00:40:08,414
只要他還帶著腳環  我們永遠無從得知
As long as he's on that anklet, we'll never know.

829
00:40:09,054 --> 00:40:10,774
我們可以在這裡坐到天荒地老
We can sit here until kingdom come

830
00:40:10,774 --> 00:40:12,574
辯論尼爾·卡夫瑞到底何許人也
and debate over who is Neal Caffrey.

831
00:40:13,234 --> 00:40:15,304
但只要我們還在栓著他
But as long as we keep him tethered,

832
00:40:15,304 --> 00:40:17,354
只要我們還視他為罪犯
as long as we treat him like a criminal,

833
00:40:18,104 --> 00:40:19,794
他就會永遠以為他真的是
He'll always think that he is one.

834
00:40:21,454 --> 00:40:25,754
無論尼爾是公民  是線人  還是竊賊
Whether Neal is a citizen, a C.I., or a thief

835
00:40:26,364 --> 00:40:29,454
這個決定必須要他自己來下
is a decision that needs to be put in his hands.

836
00:40:30,294 --> 00:40:31,074
博爾克探員
Agent Burke...

837
00:40:31,304 --> 00:40:34,684
-你好  -尼爾·卡夫瑞應該得到減刑嗎
- Hello?  - Should Neal Caffrey's sentence be commuted?

838
00:40:42,364 --> 00:40:43,204
是的
Yes.

839
00:40:44,254 --> 00:40:46,144
我認為尼爾應該得到自由
I'm saying Neal should be free.

840
00:40:47,814 --> 00:40:48,974
抱歉  事態緊急
I'm sorry -- this couldn't wait.

841
00:40:49,554 --> 00:40:51,014
彼得  卡夫瑞剪掉了腳環
Peter Caffrey's cut his anklet.

842
00:40:52,174 --> 00:40:52,864
尼爾走了
Neal's gone.


